---Use the handle with [GET_SHAPE_TEST_RESULT](#\_0x3D87450E15D98694) or [GET_SHAPE_TEST_RESULT_INCLUDING_MATERIAL](#\_0x65287525D951F6BE) until it returns 0 or 2.
